description:
Make-A-Wish, Disney and MrBeast, along with YouTube and some of the world’s top creators, came together to grant wishes for 40 Make-A-Wish children with creator-inspired wishes at the ultimate Halloween experience at Disneyland Resort.    

Disney continues to dream up exciting new ways to help make wishes come true, granting a wish every hour of every day for children facing critical illnesses.

Learn More at Joy.Disney.com
